This folder contains code samples showing the basic use of the fairgwr package.

It is encouraged to familiarize yourself first with the main "fairgwr_main.R"
routine, as this is the one that will generate the results used in virtually
every other routine.

Also included is the "autogwr" routine, showcasing an assistant automating
the generation of results for a given dataset. This can be used from R
with source("autogwr.R") or, if running Windows, directly from the autogwr.bat
file.
